### ================== RUTAS SIN AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los pagos (SIN token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/public

### Obtener pago por ID (SIN token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/public/1

### Crear un nuevo pago (SIN token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointment_id": 6,
  "amount": 50000,
  "method": "efectivo",
  "date": "2025-10-25T12:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "pendiente"
}

### Actualizar un pago (SIN token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/public/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointment_id": 6,
  "amount": 60000,
  "method": "tarjeta",
  "date": "2025-10-26T15:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "pagado"
}

