DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/public/1

### Cancelar un pago (SIN token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/public/2/cancel

### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los pagos (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener pago por ID (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un nuevo pago (CON token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointment_id": 2,
  "amount": 75000,
  "method": "transferencia",
  "date": "2025-10-25T14:30:00.000Z",
  "status": "pendiente"
}

### Actualizar un pago (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointment_id": 2,
  "amount": 80000,
  "method": "tarjeta",
  "date": "2025-10-26T16:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "pagado"
}

### Eliminar un pago físicamente (CON token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancelar un pago (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
